Learn how to use Smart Objects in Photoshop and how they protect your pixels when scaling images.
Deke McClellan is back once again to guest host with Bert Monroy on the topic of Smart Obects. We will work with RAW dng images and some type in a branding project. Screen cap (1280x720 135 KB):  &lt;a href=&quot;
http://bayimg.com/BAEekaaCP&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
